snippet.title: M.Bronx Music
snippet.description:
Every song M.Bronx creates starts with the purity of a piano and his voice.  Originally known for his dynamic writing and productions, M.Bronx  caught the attention of Jay-Z’s RocNation where he is signed as a writer and producer.  Bronx has written and produced for some of the biggest artists in the world, most notably, Beyonce, Rihanna, Nick Jonas, Demi Lovato and Billy Currington all in the last year alone. While writing for others Bronx has spent this past year Quietly crafting his own artist project that he plans to slowly release into the world.  

M.Bronx got his start in EDM where he wrote and featured on numerous tracks: "Leaving You" with Audien, "Souls" with Borgeous,  "All That We are Living For" with Hardwell,  "Against the World" with Morgan page, "Felt this good" with Kap Slap and "Saints & Sinners" with Thomas Gold.
